// Before that year, Java Time and Joda Time are not consistent with java.sql.Date and java.util.Calendar
// Since January 1, 1900 in one zone is still December 31, 1899 in some other zone, we are adding 1 year margin.
MODERN_YEAR = 1901

MODERN_YEAR_MILLIS_UTC = LocalDate.of(MODERN_YEAR,1,1)...........

Then you can inline modernDate

